TENANT 1: Show compassion and kindness to all those you meet.
TENANT 2: Keep detailed records of your journeys and interactions. Knowledge is power.
TENANT 3: Keep no personal wealth. Whenever possible, give to those less fortunate.
TENANT 4: Never seek violence, but do not flee from it. Never take a life unless in self defense.
TENANT 5: Obey all laws, rules and regulations in your travels. In foreign lands, you are our ambassadors.
TENANT 6: Always announce yourself to local Order lodges upon arriving in a new city if one is established.
TENANT 7: Never do anything that is in direct conflict with your mission or the goals of the Order.
TENANT 8: Above all, the \C[4]Triumvirate\C[0] has final and absolute authority.
